- oni2: https://github.com/onivim/oni2
  A mix of vscode and neovim
  Onivim 2 uses neovim to manage buffers and provide authentic modal editing, and features a fast, native front-end. In addition, Onivim 2 leverages the VSCode Extension Host process in its entirety - meaning, eventually, complete support for VSCode extensions and configuration.
